{
  "stem": "5639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Another characteristic thing about my mother's family was-- which was unusual for Jewish, Jewish any class family-- that the daughters had higher educations, but not the sons.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all acquired before I was born.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was due, mainly, to my grandfather who was a very broad-minded man, and he was actually one of the founder of the first Jewish boys' high school, Yavne.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yavne.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather's name was-- wait a second-- Hanoch, because I had been named after him, Erlich.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Erlich.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think there was another name, but I forgot-- Shia-- Shia Hanoch, or Hanoch Shia-- something like that-- Erlich.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, God-- Makes you realize how many things you forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he died very young, considerably young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the legend in our times, in our family, went that--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the legend in our family went that he was a very heavy smoker.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came from a long chain of tobacco merchants, and his own father was known-- out part of Poland was belonging, at times, to Russia, at times to Austro-Hungarian monarchy.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was in times of Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the fame of his skill of mixing various tobaccos were as far as Moscow, and he was getting orders from the officers to send them tobacco.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I still remember a stair leading from my grandmother's kitchen with a door, and that was leading to the shop.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was to go at night, when everybody was asleep, and prepare his mixtures.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they ask him, when will you give us the recipe?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, before I die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And lo and behold, he dropped dead without giving anybody the-- [LAUGHS] the recipe for the--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my grandfather, actually, very soon abandoned the tobacco business.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
